metadata.name: Transcendent Gear Cats
metadata.description:
Style transfer was used to produce 2000 images of Leopards, Cheetahs, and Tigers made out of gears. Then a generative adversarial network was trained on these images for 3 days. An interpolation video was generated in order to animate inside of the network.

Length: 26 second
Resolution: 1080x1080p
Audio: Jeremy Torman
